# --- Build artifacts ---
# Go
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.test
*.out

# Binaries produced by `go build`
/forge
/forge.exe
/dist/
/build/

# --- Spec / internal docs (not for public repo) ---
# Keep the build spec and the live per-phase status logs out
# of version control. The user-facing record of each phase
# lives in README.md and the commit messages; PHASE_*.md
# files are private working notes that should not be
# pushed to GitHub.
FORGE_BUILD_SPEC.md
/docs/internal/
PHASE_*.md

# AGENTS.md is the private build-handoff document for AI agents
# working on this repo. It encodes the architecture, conventions,
# and phase methodology so a fresh agent can pick up the build.
# It is intentionally not published to GitHub — the public record
# of how to use Forge lives in README.md.
AGENTS.md

# --- Editor / OS noise ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Claude Code state (local-only, not part of the project) ---
# The .claude/ directory is Claude Code's per-repo runtime state
# (permission allowlists, session logs, agent files, etc.). It is
# not part of the project's source and is intentionally kept out
# of version control so that the project's GitHub identity stays
# clean of Claude Code internals.
.claude/

# --- Secrets / env ---
.env
.env.local
*.pem
*.key

# --- Go workspace / vendor (if used later) ---
vendor/
go.work
go.work.sum
